    library(lme4)

    ## Loading required package: Matrix

    mixed = lmer(value~time+(1|location),data = med_exp,REML = TRUE)
    summary(mixed)

    ## Linear mixed model fit by REML ['lmerMod']
    ## Formula: value ~ time + (1 | location)
    ##    Data: med_exp
    ## 
    ## REML criterion at convergence: 4180
    ## 
    ## Scaled residuals: 
    ##     Min      1Q  Median      3Q     Max 
    ## -4.2495 -0.5296  0.0047  0.5434  4.3759 
    ## 
    ## Random effects:
    ##  Groups   Name        Variance Std.Dev.
    ##  location (Intercept) 3.9039   1.9758  
    ##  Residual             0.5706   0.7554  
    ## Number of obs: 1712, groups:  location, 52
    ## 
    ## Fixed effects:
    ##               Estimate Std. Error t value
    ## (Intercept) -1.994e+02  2.995e+00  -66.56
    ## time         1.030e-01  1.489e-03   69.18
    ## 
    ## Correlation of Fixed Effects:
    ##      (Intr)
    ## time -0.996

    #Inference for random term - location
    non_loc = lm(value~time,data = med_exp)
    library(RLRsim)
    exactLRT(mixed,non_loc)

    ## No restrictions on fixed effects. REML-based inference preferable.

    ## Using likelihood evaluated at REML estimators.

    ## Please refit model with method="ML" for exact results.

    ## 
    ##  simulated finite sample distribution of LRT. (p-value based on 10000
    ##  simulated values)
    ## 
    ## data:  
    ## LRT = 3055.7, p-value < 2.2e-16

    plot(fitted(mixed),resid(mixed,type='pearson'))
